data.description: Welcome to this incredible garage townhome! As you enter, you'll be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors that span the main level, adding a touch of warmth and sophistication. The gourmet chef's kitchen is a standout feature, boasting granite countertops, raised panel cabinets, and top stainless steel appliances, including a Sub-Zero refrigerator. Entertaining is a breeze in the open floor plan with a separate dining room, while the light-filled living room has large French doors that lead to a spacious two-story deck - the perfect spot for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the peaceful surroundings. This home offers two primary suites complete with custom shelving and cedar closets, upgraded light fixtures, and new flooring. The loft retreat is a versatile space, featuring skylights and ample storage, ideal for creating a cozy reading nook or functional home office. Downstairs, the finished lower level boasts high ceilings, a bathroom, and sliding French doors that open onto a brick patio and fully fenced private yard, providing additional space for relaxation and entertainment. Freshly painted and updated throughout, this home offers exceptional value. Any offers Will be reviewed by noon on Thursday 4/18/2024
